Dialogue: 0, 0:00:00.00, 0:00:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在广袤的草原上，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}正端坐一旁
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:02.96, 0:00:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}神情{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}专注地监工。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:04.62, 0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他吩咐{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}士兵{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}们开始挖坑，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:06.66, 0:00:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,准备搭建巨大的加温{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}容器{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:08.89, 0:00:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}阳光{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}洒在草原上，士兵们开始忙碌地
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:11.84, 0:00:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,挖掘横竖三丈的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}大坑{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:13.69, 0:00:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,每个{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}相距{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}不得超过半丈，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:15.73, 0:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,中间还要挖出{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}竖坑{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:17.39, 0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}继续在坑边指导士兵加固坑
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:20.25, 0:00:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,壁，他看着已经挖好的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}大坑{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:22.72, 0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,思考着如何加固以抗{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}高温{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:25.00, 0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,草原上，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}高岭土{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}随处可见，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:27.28, 0:00:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵们忙着将{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}高岭土{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}过筛、
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:29.57, 0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加水搅拌制成{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}陶泥{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:31.28, 0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}准备{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}糊在坑壁上。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:32.81, 0:00:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,三日后，帅帐内，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}端坐其中，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:35.83, 0:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}侯君集{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}、薛仁贵、北向辉三人围坐。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:38.85, 0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}侯君集{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}率先开口，向李承乾汇报唐军
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:41.87, 0:00:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,已距{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}诺真{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}水河不足二十里，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:44.14, 0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,估计一日后将与{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}薛延陀{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}大军交战。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:46.96, 0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}薛仁贵{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}和北向辉对视一眼，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:49.21, 0:00:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}薛仁贵{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}起身向李承乾汇报，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:51.46, 0:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,称{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世绩{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}大军粮草不济，
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:53.51, 0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}灶火{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}已由每日二燃变为每日一燃。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:56.32, 0:00:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,北向辉在旁{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}补充{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}确认。
Dialogue: 0, 0:00:58.20, 0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}询问侯君集薛延陀兵力及统
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:00.91, 0:01:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,军将领情况，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}侯君集{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}回应薛延陀人马
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:03.81, 0:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,约十二万，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}统军{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}主帅是大度设。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:06.34, 0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}接着询问侯君集对大度设统
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:09.04, 0:01:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,兵能力的看法，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}侯君集{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}自信表示有信
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:11.95, 0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,心{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}应对{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:12.67, 0:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这时一名{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}士兵{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}进入帐内，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:14.76, 0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,报告称城外有人奉{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}漠南{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}行军总管帅
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:17.64, 0:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,令前来{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}调粮{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:18.78, 0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}听后一笑，让士兵将调粮之人
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:21.84, 0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}领进来{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:22.60, 0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,调粮{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}士兵{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}进入帐中，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:24.18, 0:01:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,见到{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}后惊讶不已，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:26.10, 0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}结结巴巴{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}地说着调粮之事。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:28.21, 0:01:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}则笑眯眯地回应，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:30.14, 0:01:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让士兵回去转告{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世绩{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:32.06, 0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,自己这里也不{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}富裕{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:33.65, 0:01:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,若有需要可来{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}云中{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}都督府，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:35.75, 0:01:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}管饱{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:36.62, 0:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世绩{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}得知李承乾在云中都督府后
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:39.40, 0:01:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,，十分震惊，他难以相信{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}能如此
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:42.56, 0:01:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,迅速地{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}出现{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}在那里。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:44.23, 0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,此时，哨骑又来{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}报告{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}大度设已率三万
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:47.20, 0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,兵屯于{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}诺真{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}水河以南，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:49.06, 0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}情况危急{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:50.00, 0:01:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世绩{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}在军中思考后，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:51.90, 0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,决定{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}原地{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}扎营以威慑大度设，
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:54.39, 0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,同时修书八百里加急呈交{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}朝廷{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}请求
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:57.25, 0:01:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}粮草{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}支援。
Dialogue: 0, 0:01:58.21, 0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太极殿内，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}端坐龙椅，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:00.62, 0:02:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,面色阴沉，因收到{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}占据云中都
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:03.59, 0:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}督府{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}等消息而愤怒。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:05.26, 0:02:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他询问{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}唐俭{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}粮草最快多久能运至前
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:08.05, 0:02:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,线，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}唐俭{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}回应最快半月。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:10.09, 0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}要求七天内运到，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:12.12, 0:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}唐俭{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}表示不可能。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:13.62, 0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,长孙无忌提出让朝廷给{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}修书
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:16.31, 0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,，让其出兵援救{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世绩{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}大军，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:18.67, 0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}愤怒表示不会求那个逆子，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:21.37, 0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还下令让{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李靖{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}火速率军进攻云中擒
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:24.06, 0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,拿{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:24.96, 0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,魏征等大臣劝谏{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}收回旨意，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:27.84, 0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}虽冲动但最终收回旨意，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:30.52, 0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}众人{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}跪地叩头称陛下英明。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:32.81, 0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}长孙{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}无忌打圆场，商议由中书省拟旨
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:35.82, 0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}出兵援救，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:37.51, 0:02:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李世民{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}不情不愿地同意，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:39.57, 0:02:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}退朝{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}离去。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:40.51, 0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,远在云中都督府的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:42.75, 0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,正忙于造纸{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}大业{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，双手被纸浆浸泡得
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:45.75, 0:02:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,腐烂{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}脱皮{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
