Dialogue: 0, 0:02:48.92, 0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他看着自己的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}双手{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:50.61, 0:02:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,露出无奈的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}神情{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
