Dialogue: 0, 0:02:53.78, 0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看到晾晒好的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}纸张{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:55.45, 0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,露出满意的{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}神情{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}。
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:56.94, 0:02:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这时{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}侯君集{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}三人疾步走来，
Dialogue: 0, 0:02:59.18, 0:03:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,告知{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}陛下恢复其太子之位的
Dialogue: 0, 0:03:01.97, 0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,消息，{\c&H0000FFFF&\b1}李承乾{\c&H00FFFFFF&\b0}露出惊讶的神情。
